Package org.strykeforce.thirdcoast.telemetry

Provides a data streaming service for robot sensors, actuators or subsystems.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Inventory
    Represents the inventory of robot hardware and subsystems that can have telemetry streaming.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractInventory
    An abstract base class intended to be subclassed by concrete implmentations of Inventory.
    InventoryModule
    Dagger dependency-injection support for Inventory.
    NetworkModule
    Dagger dependency-injection support for networking configuration.
    RobotInventory
    Default implementation of Inventory for a robot.
    TelemetryController
    Provides a web service to control telemetry.
    TelemetryService
    The Telemetry service registers Item instances for data collection and controls the starting and stopping of the service.

Package org.strykeforce.thirdcoast.telemetry Description

Provides a data streaming service for robot sensors, actuators or subsystems. Documentation for client-server communication is here.
